title: In the Studio: AHMAD JAMAL Part One
fulltitle: In the Studio: AHMAD JAMAL Part One
description:
Watch and listen to pianist and composer Ahmad Jamal speak to us about his music, his life, and his experience working with Jazz at Lincoln Center. 

For more videos, subscribe today to the Jazz at Lincoln Center channel: http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCP108sGgYT_TlG2YRColGcg?sub_confirmation=1
To learn more about Jazz at Lincoln Center, visit us at http://www.jalc.org
